        Using the Neighbour's Recent Sale as a Comparable: How Brisbane Sellers Handle the Next-Door Reference
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        When the house next door sells, the result becomes the dominant reference point. Here's how to use it as one comparable among several, rather than letting a single number anchor everything.
      </p>
    </div>
